## Runtime (Desktop + Cloud)

```
Electron/Browser â†’ React â†’ apiClient (/api/v1) â†’ Express â†’ modules (routesâ†’servicesâ†’repositories) â†’ FinancialPostingService â†’ PostgreSQL
